citations:
    citation-agot-bran-iv:
        source: source-agot
        properties:
            locator: "Bran IV"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Tyrion Lannister visits Winterfell and presents a design for a special saddle that will allow the crippled Bran to ride. Tyrion tells Bran Jon Snow asked him to help. Robb Stark is suspicious of Tyrion's motives. Tyrion says he has 'a tender spot in my heart for cripples and bastards and broken things.' Theon Greyjoy laughs at Bran's distress. Maester Luwin accepts the saddle design."
